column2: Ship has been badly hit by enemy aircraft and may explode any minute. Crew left it a few hours ago.
The ship has been hit by aerial bombs, but is still fully functional and evacuation seems to be a bad call of its captain.
The ship has been repeatedly hit by enemy artillery fire. It's hard to tell why it wasn't sunk by the attacker.
